s and children became sedentary, and they didn\rquote t travel, because the men would go off trucking, but be back in a fortnight. Motorisation, in fact, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid16274490 
